{"tid":1854762,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"派香艷福利賀年　陳婉衡晒36E益觀眾","createTime":"2020-01-31T16:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T16:08:56.000Z","uid":44730,"like":11,"dislike":158,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"839d5738d88aa189a47c2a0240b79c93dda683b8","tid":1854762,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐，好多人都減少外出，最好安坐家中睇「咪神」陳婉衡(Alycia)新春大派福利。事關嚟緊周日晚，佢同尤蔭蔭喺《識玩旅行團2》壓軸篇中會穿上性感泳衣亮相，凸顯36E最強「胸器」，大家關注疫情及瘋搶口罩同時，火辣辣嘅Alycia都可以幫到大家鬆一鬆，醒醒神。至於本周六晚嘅《3日2夜》，佢就會同簡淑兒(Jessica)遊走英國貝爾法斯特㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200131/_2020013120205445523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200131%2F_2020013120205445523.jpg&h=6a64af9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6e8509ec06708546fb23fa3aed4cd0d9a6a8e01","tid":1854762,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":57,"score":-57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200131/_2020013120205729550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200131%2F_2020013120205729550.jpg&h=d8679e59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相對陳婉衡，尤蔭蔭身材失色咗小小。"},{"pid":"b38b82cc8cf7244bf3074ea89a97047d866189bb","tid":1854762,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":76,"score":-73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200131/_2020013120205985144.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200131%2F_2020013120205985144.jpg&h=5876528c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n穿上粉色Top完全擋不住36E驕人身材。"},{"pid":"408eea51cc15a6d81bad69f3775bbe7d94bce463","tid":1854762,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3a84ef7d303861b8cd2c4fd49c2191bedbaaaa","tid":1854762,"uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"第二輯嘅《識玩旅行團》壓軸篇交波畀區永權、陳婉衡、尤蔭蔭，節目中Alycia會介紹珠海一間酒店，當然唔少得親身體驗酒店內的室內暖水泳池，三位主持人同時撲落水，令節目生色不少。陳婉衡說：「今次我哋去咗廣州三江自治區、珠海及澳門，但行程好難忘呀！因為天氣不似預期，突然凍到得返幾度，搞到團友們要喺當地買外衣、頸巾同手襪保暖，好彩泳池係室內暖水池唔會太凍。最值得一讚係今次行程安排得好好，我哋先拍晒泳裝鏡頭，打後的全部係『食好西』，咁就冇後顧之憂，而且最正係泳池隔離係健身室，我哋着住浴袍最後衝刺，不停咁加操，要以最Fit姿態示人。」"},{"pid":"25fbf95712ef5fe80785bb1a1b063520b65084b5","tid":1854762,"uid":80679,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"839d5738d88aa189a47c2a0240b79c93dda683b8","tid":1854762,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐，好多人都減少外出，最好安坐家中睇「咪神」陳婉衡(Alycia)新春大派福利。事關嚟緊周日晚，佢同尤蔭蔭喺《識玩旅行團2》壓軸篇中會穿上性感泳衣亮相，凸顯36E最強「胸器」，大家關注疫情及瘋搶口罩同時，火辣辣嘅Alycia都可以幫到大家鬆一鬆，醒醒神。至於本周六晚嘅《3日2夜》，佢就會同簡淑兒(Jessica)遊走英國貝爾法斯特㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200131/_2020013120205445523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200131%2F_2020013120205445523.jpg&h=6a64af9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:13:26.000Z","msg":"我就訓<br />\n唔想打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecae66f8cab191e48656f219978fe9cb9bf596e","tid":1854762,"uid":133424,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"睇錯陳婉嫻"},{"pid":"18c16f60650d3ee601045fd024ac385330cc757e","tid":1854762,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"<strong>自爆有乳貼防護</strong><br />\n當日陳婉衡穿上粉色top，豐滿上圍「呼之肉出」，尤蔭蔭明顯比下去。Alycia說：「唔係呀！蔭蔭着嘅紅色比堅尼好靚，我嗰件唔係三角bra top款，相對比較安全同保守，曾經試過走光，經驗之談，為咗工作會揀件穩陣泳衣，仲要加埋乳貼嚟做最後保護防線，始終泳衣塊布好細，大啲動作都唔安全。因為每人身形唔同，最緊要搵件fit身嘅，我對自己身形要求比較高，話晒係一個健身教練，唔能夠拆自己招牌嘛。」講到新年願望，Alycia除咗希望自己同家人都身體健康外，今年有幾個健身project，希望可以順順利利。"},{"pid":"0d2c41c37f3fa095ceb5b06fa9ad228af59e7346","tid":1854762,"uid":345458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:13:45.000Z","msg":"緊急⚠️⚠️冇人知今日醫護有野搞！！<br />\n幫我入去十連！！<br />\n<br />\n「全城集氣撐醫護！！」今日三個行程終極懶人包！我要所有人出嚟集氣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3636ef9038ec124fde376ce1e72e39bb18217940","tid":1854762,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":28,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200131/_2020013120210474922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200131%2F_2020013120210474922.jpg&h=37baf73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新一年傾咗幾個健身project，希望成事兼順利。"},{"pid":"0b872f719aa414f72bfb229cc3ff7e3cfd6a9d42","tid":1854762,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:14:03.000Z","msg":"好正"},{"pid":"0f07db086a24fb1e79f9cfd8f1839feab8a5deb7","tid":1854762,"uid":194415,"like":103,"dislike":6,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:15:29.000Z","msg":"比例好肉酸<br />\n係大波但係全個 BODY 睇冇美感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4461320cbe4e77fcc3abe1cbe723a0ec386ab64","tid":1854762,"uid":266755,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"我估喺石頭波"},{"pid":"b3c9c810923f5068dda21339265268596ee263d0","tid":1854762,"uid":216239,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"假波<br />\nFced"},{"pid":"54666a0728f7516ea516937ed4a2d871a8b1d820","tid":1854762,"uid":60393,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a4461320cbe4e77fcc3abe1cbe723a0ec386ab64","tid":1854762,"uid":266755,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"我估喺石頭波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:20:50.000Z","msg":"負重訓練姐"},{"pid":"479fef572ed9e9a9286b5bfd1b41773a28d668ea","tid":185